{"tid":1058222,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"近排嚟咗個新移民插班生","createTime":"2019-03-12T11:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T03:24:01.000Z","uid":64601,"like":77,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2e66109e29a2598775317be4eef292538d15d267","tid":1058222,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:42:48.000Z","msg":"是咁dick，最近嚟咗個新移民插班生。<br />\n示意圖：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEy4W6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaEy4W6e.jpg&h=5b76f172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁尋日幾個冇交功課，俾人罰抄書，咁我、凱婷同幾個fd子咪搵個插班生幫手抄書。<br />\n<br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蝗=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：喂，幫手抄書得唔得呀？<br />\nmk: 禾抄！<br />\n<br />\n見佢咁熱心咪塞本功課俾佢，其他人見佢咁抵得諗咪問埋一份，點知佢又大大聲講禾抄！禾抄！最後全班啲功課俾哂佢，臨走時仲見到佢眼濕濕好似好感動見大家咁歡迎佢。<br />\n<br />\n今日條撚屌竟然唔返，有冇知點先拎得返份功課？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346d2e38476e1b84045df4b9d501ed19735b3a75","tid":1058222,"uid":108016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"記者叫埋成班同學玩鳩隻支那狗"},{"pid":"b96f290a227bb2b3a37483a08b87d4dc3f4cf4f5","tid":1058222,"uid":59703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:44:13.000Z","msg":"禾抄"},{"pid":"1abfec8517a525bd868af88c8f992671abd6829c","tid":1058222,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651e381ec3cea5b60cd73eb515f0c7bb32e81353","tid":1058222,"uid":5150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:45:55.000Z","msg":"而家得返啲蝗會mk?"},{"pid":"0a34e9a283ae736d924d79e6ab80908d6b0af171","tid":1058222,"uid":124491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl